Worldtime,is,a,time,service,that,provides,localized,time,for,anywhere,in,the,world,through,a,search,tool,The,site,includes,the,search,function,different,time,display,options,information,about,daylight,savings,time,and,other,functions,The,Worldtime,API,uses,REST,calls,and,is,comprised,of,an,IP,address,to,time,service,and,a,latitude,to,time,service,These,allow,the,user,to,integrate,time,information,services,into,third,party,applications,An,API,key,is,required,with,service